<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resultados del Quiz - TestYourFriends</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9fafb; color: #111827; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 16px; }
    .card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .header h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .header p { color: #6b7280; margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .result-box { background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .result-box h2 { font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 4px; }
    .result-box p { color: #6b7280; margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .scores { margin: 16px 0; }
    .score-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 4px 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .score-label { color: #6b7280; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #111827; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>TestYourFriends</h1>
        <p>Resultados de la sesión {{sessionCode}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>Hola {{participantName}},</p>
      <p>Aquí están tus resultados del quiz <strong>Dilemas Éticos</strong>:</p>

      <div class="result-box">
        <h2>{{characterName}}</h2>
        <p>{{characterDescription}}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="scores">
        <div class="score-row"><span class="score-label">Pragmatismo</span><span>{{scoreP}}/10</span></div>
        <div class="score-row"><span class="score-label">Idealismo</span><span>{{scoreI}}/10</span></div>
        <div class="score-row"><span class="score-label">Empatía</span><span>{{scoreE}}/10</span></div>
        <div class="score-row"><span class="score-label">Rebeldía</span><span>{{scoreR}}/10</span></div>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="{{groupResultsUrl}}" class="btn">Ver resultados del grupo</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} TestYourFriends</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
